[{"id":"bf93c58105f1201cd95c9e00262fd6ab","from":"Hulu","from_email":"hulu@hulumail.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"We've Updated Our Privacy Policy","date":"2015-03-10T04:21:58.000Z","formatted_date":"Mar 10, 2015","formatted_time":"4:21 AM","body":"\n\nhttp://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada116ff78899342308461ddaf657aac7da8a1c00d3e76596a9d683f49bb4043b3a82 \n\n\n\n \nHi Jeffrey,\n\n \nIt's been an exciting 2014 so far at Hulu! We're thrilled with the response to our Originals (like 'The Awesomes' and 'The Hotwives of Orlando',) and have continued to acquire exciting content (like 'The Bridge' and 'Manhattan'.) Throughout 2014 and in the years to come, we remain committed to providing the best user experience possible.\n \n\nHulu has grown exponentially in its user base and its service offerings in the past few years. To best serve our valued users (including you!), we needed to update our Terms of Use.\n\n \nUpdates include:\n\n- Expanding the description of the Hulu service to ensure that we include all technology through which you can use Hulu and Hulu Plus\n\n- Incorporating the current options on your Account page\n\n- Clarifying our mutual arbitration clause and providing you with additional rights to better assist you, should the need arise\n\n- Updating our physical address since we moved to our new digs in Santa Monica, CA\n\n\n \n\nThese are the key highlights, and we encourage you to review the new Terms of Use in full at http://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada1125e435363d7ad222fa03a53714913236dfe2ea7daf080a4c85300dcd216da9f3 \n \nHulu's continued success would not be possible without users like you. If you have any questions regarding our updated Terms of Use, don't hesitate to contact us at legal@hulu.com.\n\n\n \nSincerely,\n\nYour friends at Hulu\n\n \n\nFollow Us \nhttp://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada114d6dab4b0c26e6bb37945d556dbf344b895c23822d70394aa3fdff6477b3bf75 \nhttp://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada1175f544f39b1d84ce69971e35618d3692dab504411ef11efe9671e6a722a408c8 \n\nContact Us\nhttp://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada11fe7a5160ee5fe91f92430409bd6b613845e052aff37e77ea7dc41ea588320cf3 \n\nHulu. 2500 Broadway, 2nd Floor, Santa Monica, CA 90404\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd\">\n<html>\n<head>\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">\n.appleLinks a {color:#a5a5a5; text-decoration: none;}\n    .appleLinksWhite a {color:#ffffff; text-decoration: none;}\n* {\n\tmargin-top: 0px;\n\tmargin-bottom: 0px;\n\tpadding: 0px;\n\tborder: none;\n\tline-height: normal;\n\toutline: none;\n\tlist-style: none;\n\tfont-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\n\t-webkit-text-size-adjust: none;\n\t-ms-text-size-adjust:none;\n\t\n}\n\nbody {\n\tmargin-top: 0 !important;\n\tmargin-bottom: 0 !important;\n\tpadding-top: 0 !important;\n\tpadding-bottom: 0 !important;\n\twidth: 100% !important;\n\t-webkit-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;\n\t-ms-text-size-adjust: 100% !important;\n\t-webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased !important;\n\t\n}\nimg {\n\tborder: 0 !important;\n\t\n\toutline: none !important;\n}\ntd {\n\tborder-collapse: collapse !important;\n\tmso-line-height-rule: exactly;\n}\ntable {\n\tborder-collapse: collapse !important;\n\tmso-table-lspace: 0pt;\n\tmso-table-rspace: 0pt;\n}\ntd  .desktop_hide{\n\tdisplay:none !important;\n\tmso-hide: all; /* hide elements in Outlook 2007-2013 */\n\n\t}\n td .desktop_hide_bg{\n\tdisplay:none !important;\n\tmso-hide: all; /* hide elements in Outlook 2007-2013 */ (optional)\n\t\n\t\n\t}\n\n@media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {\ntable[class=wrapper] {\n\twidth: 100% !important;\n}\ntable[class=main_table] {\n\twidth: 310px !important;\n}\n