;\n\t }\n}\n</style>\n</head>\n\n<body marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#eeeeee\" style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; background-repeat: repeat; width: 100% !important; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color:595959;\" offset=\"0\" topmargin=\"0\" leftmargin=\"0\"><style type=\"text/css\">\ndiv.preheader \n{ display: none !important; } \n</style>\n<div class=\"preheader\" style=\"font-size: 1px; display: none !important;\">From Your Friends at Hulu</div>\n\n<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#eeeeee\" class=\"wrapper\">\n<tr>\n\t<td align=\"center\">\n\t\t<table width=\"640\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" class=\"main_table\">\n\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t<td height=\"20\">\n\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t<td style=\"color:#999999;font-size:20px\" valign=\"top\" align = \"left\">\n\t\t\t\t<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"main_table\">\n <tr>\n                \t<td height=\"15\"></td>\n                </tr><tr>\n                                  <td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style = \"padding-bottom: 8px; padding-top: 8px;\">\n                                 <table border=\"0\" align=\"left\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" >\n                                    <tr>\n                                      <td class = \"header\" width=\"20\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"></td>\n        \t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"><a href=\"http://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada11483b84c7c57cebf900d2449864b01849875e109dd6def2718234021193a04285\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://assets.hulu.com/emails/Hulu_Logo_PNG_128x42.png\" alt=\"Hulu\" width=\"64\" height=\"21\" border=\"0\" style=\"display:block; font-size:15px; font-weight:bold; background-color:#eeeeee; font-weight:bold; color:#66aa33;\" /></a></td>\n                                    \n                                  </table>\n                              \n                                  \n                                  </td>\n                                </tr>\n</table>\n\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t<td height=\"20\"></td>\n\t\t\t</tr>\n\n\n\n<tr>\n\t<td align=\"center\">\n\t\t<table width=\"640\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#ffffff\" style=\"border: 1px solid #d4d4d4; border-radius:5px\" class=\"main_table\">\n\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t<table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"chnge\">\n                        <table width=\"593\" class=\"wrapper\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n                     <tr><td height=\"30\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <td align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:'Arial', 'Arial', sans-serif;font-size:14px; color:#666666; line-height:22px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none;\">Hi Jeffrey,                      \n\t\t\t\t\t  </tr>\n                      <tr><td height=\"15\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <td align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:'Arial', 'Arial', sans-serif;font-size:14px; color:#666666; line-height:22px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none;\">\n                     2015 is in full swing, and here at Hulu we're looking forward to our most exciting year yet. As we continually strive to bring you the best viewing experience anywhere, we want to ensure that we keep you informed about practices related to our relationship with you, our viewer.</tr>\n                      <tr><td height=\"15\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <td align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:'Arial', 'Arial', sans-serif;font-size:14px; color:#666666; line-height:22px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none;\">\n                     We respect your privacy and want to be transparent about what we do with your information. We have updated our Privacy Policy to clarify what information from or about you we collect, use and share. \n                      </tr>\n                      \n                       <tr><td height=\"15\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <td align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:'Arial', 'Arial', sans-serif;font-size:14px; color:#666666; line-height:22px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none;\">Updates include:\n                      </tr>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <td align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:'Arial', 'Arial', sans-serif;font-size:14px; color:#666666; line-height:22px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none; padding-left:20px;\">&bull;&nbsp;We've simplified and reorganized the structure, making it easier for you to find and review relevant sections. (e.g., we've incorporated clickable section headings that link directly to the corresponding sections of the policy.)<br>\n&bull;&nbsp;We've incorporated opt-out options into relevant sections about the use, collection and disclosure of information from or about you, making it easier for you to choose how your information is managed.<br>\n&bull;&nbsp;To provide you with another notification option when it comes to your privacy, we will now email you about material changes to our Privacy Policy if you have provided us with a current email address<br>\n                      </tr>\n                      \n                       <tr><td height=\"15\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <td align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:'Arial', 'Arial', sans-serif;font-size:14px; color:#666666; line-height:22px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none;\">\n                   While these are some key highlights, we encourage you to read the new Privacy Policy in full at <a href=\"http://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada11b1c3a04c163f036eec678c967e6d3dd7fcc678be4b92215a8140ebfe6a8c48a0\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height:22px; color:#3377bb; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold;\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hulu.com/privacy</a></tr>\n                      \n                               <tr><td height=\"15\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <td align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:'Arial', 'Arial', sans-serif;font-size:14px; color:#666666; line-height:22px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none;\">\nWe're thrilled that you are a part of Hulu in 2015, and if you have any questions feel free to drop us a line at <a href=\"mailto:legal@hulu.com\" style=\"font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height:22px; color:#3377bb; text-decoration:none; font-weight:bold;\" target=\"_blank\">legal@hulu.com</a>\n                      </tr>\n                      \n                      \n                               <tr><td height=\"15\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t  <td align=\"left\" style=\"font-family:'Arial', 'Arial', sans-serif;font-size:14px; color:#666666; line-height:22px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none;\">\n                  Sincerely,\n<br>\nYour friends at Hulu\n                      </tr>\n                       <tr><td height=\"30\">&nbsp;</td></tr>\n                      \n                    </table>\n\n                    </td></tr></table>\n\t\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t</table>\n\t</td>\n</tr>\n <tr>\n<td height=\"15\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n    <td align=\"center\"><table width=\"230\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\" class=\"wrapper\">\n      <tr>\n        <td><table width=\"230\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n          <tr>\n            <td><table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n              <tr>\n                <td width=\"83\" valign=\"bottom\" style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif ;font-size:14px; font-weight:bold; color:#999999;\" align=\"right\"><a style=\"text-decoration:none; color:#999999;\">Follow Us</a></td>\n                 <td width=\"7\">&nbsp;</td>\n                <td width=\"20\" valign=\"top\"><a href=\"http://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada11161395c2219525dcc6d03e3cbf11e29b4dc34a30464493a85f50dbf8aec2c0d4\"><img src=\"http://assets.hulu.com/emails/facebook_icon.gif\" alt=\"Facebook\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" style=\"display:block; border:none;\" /></a></td>\n                <td width=\"7\">&nbsp;</td>\n                <td width=\"20\" valign=\"top\"><a href=\"http://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada1168f90343f3f7f15ab55c9f28fe7b27f17dceb4fe380a9e6457799b33797a3784\"><img src=\"http://assets.hulu.com/emails/twitter_icon.gif\" alt=\"Twitter\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" style=\"display:block; border:none;\" /></a></td>\n                <td width=\"17\">&nbsp;</td>\n                <td align=\"center\" width=\"3\" valign=\"bottom\" style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif ;font-size:14px; font-weight:bold; color:#666666;\">|</td>\n<td width=\"17\">&nbsp;</td>\n                <td align=\"left\" valign=\"bottom\" style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif ;font-size:14px; font-weight:bold; color:#999999;\"><a href=\"http://click.hulumail.com/?qs=fc7a522e205ada11d2e962272c754cc4ed0afbaff8954739ed869865fd0380366a6f41f9f535ae96\" style=\"text-decoration:none; color:#999999;\">Help</a></td>\n              </tr>\n            </table></td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td height=\"15\" style=\"font-size:1px; line-height:1px;\">&nbsp;</td>\n          </tr>\n        </table></td>\n      </tr>\n    </table></td>\n  </tr>\n \n  <tr>\n    <td style=\"font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif ;font-size:11px; color:#a5a5a5; text-align:center;\"><span class=\"appleLinks\">Hulu. 2500 Broadway, 2nd Floor, Santa Monica, CA 90404</span></t